label.value: Reduced acetylglucosamine-6-sulfate sulfatase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Concentration or activity of N-acetylglucosamine-6-sulfatase (EC 3.1.6.14) as measured in cultured fibroblasts is below the limits of normal. N-acetylglucosamine-6-sulfatase hydrolyzes heparan sulfate and keratan sulfate.
Activity or concentration of in the level of porphobilinogen deaminase (EC 4.3.1.8) in erythrocytes below the lower limit of normal.

label.value: Reduced holocarboxylase synthetase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Concentration or activity of holocarboxylase synthetase (EC 6.3.4.10) as measured in cultured fibroblasts is below the limits of normal.
Concentration or activity of alpha mannosidase outside of the limits of normal in the blood circulation.
Concentration or activity of alpha-N-acetylgalactosaminidase (EC 3.2.1.49) is below the limits of normal. The activity can be measured in multiple tissues including cultured fibroblasts.
Activity or concentration of arginase (EC 3.5.3.1) in red blood cells below the lower limit of normal. Arginase catalyzes the last step of the urea cycle.

label.value: Reduced mitochondrial acetyl-CoA acetyltransferase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Concentration or activity of mitochondrial acetyl-CoA acetyltransferase (EC 2.3.1.9) as measured in cultured fibroblasts is below the limits of normal.
Concentration or activity of beta-mannosidase (EC 3.2.1.25) below the lower limit of normal. Beta-mannosidas enzyme can be measured in multiple tissues including leukocytes and cultured fibroblasts.

label.value: Reduced 3-methylcrotonyl CoA carboxylase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Activity of 3-methylcrotonyl-CoA carboxylase (EC 6.4.1.4) below the lower limit of normal in cultured fibroblasts.

label.value: Reduced branched-chain alpha-keto acid dehydrogenase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Activity of branched-chain alpha-keto acid dehydrogenase complex (EC 1.2.4.4) below the lower limit of normal in cultured fibroblasts.
Activity or concentration of in the level of galactose-1-phosphate uridylyltransferase (GALT; EC 2.7.7.12) in erythrocytes below the lower limit of normal.
Activity of adenosine deaminase in red blood cells outside the limits of normal.

label.value: Reduced isovaleryl CoA dehydrogenase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Activity of isovaleryl-CoA dehydrogenase (EC 1.3.99.10) below the lower limit of normal in cultured fibroblasts.

label.value: Reduced glycerol kinase activity in cultured fibroblasts

definition.value: Activity of glycerol kinase (EC 2.7.1.30) below the lower limit of normal in cultured fibroblasts.
Concentration of vitamin A above the upper limit of normal in the blood circulation.
Concentration of hyaluronic acid in the blood circulation above the upper limit of normal.
